---
<Base
	title="Slax Note — AI 음성 노트. 당신은 말하고, 저는 적습니다."
	description="당신은 말하고, 저는 적습니다. 한 번의 녹음이 선택한 프롬프트에 따라 다양한 모습으로 다듬어집니다. 해를 거듭하며 여러분과 함께 성장하도록 만들어졌습니다."
	ogImage="/og/note.png"
	schema={schema}
>
	<Nav active="note" />

	<main>
		<!-- HERO -->
		<section class="n-hero">
			<div class="n-hero-inner">
				<div>
					<h1 class="n-h1">
						AI 음성 노트. <em>당신은 말하고, 저는 적습니다.</em>
					</h1>
					<ul class="n-bullets">
						<li>떠오르는 그 순간, 바로 말로 남기십시오. 타이핑도, 정리도 필요 없습니다.</li>
						<li>한 번의 녹음, 다양한 모습 — 선택한 프롬프트에 따라 다듬어집니다.</li>
						<li>해를 거듭하며 여러분과 함께 성장하도록 만들어졌습니다.</li>
					</ul>
					<div class="n-stores">
						<a
							class="store-btn is-primary"
							href="https://apps.apple.com/us/app/slax-note-transcribe-voice-pen/id6480166286"
							target="_blank"
							rel="noopener noreferrer"
						>
							<span class="store-small">Download on the</span>
							<span class="store-main">App Store</span>
						</a>
						<a
							class="store-btn"
							href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=app.slax.notes"
							target="_blank"
							rel="noopener noreferrer"
						>
							<span class="store-small">GET IT ON</span>
							<span class="store-main">Google Play</span>
						</a>
					</div>
					<p class="n-web-link">
						또는 <a href="https://n.slax.com/">웹 버전 열기</a>.
					</p>
				</div>
				<div class="n-visual">
					<img
						src="/images/note/cover.png"
						alt="Slax Note — AI 음성 노트"
						class="n-img"
						loading="eager"
					/>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- EFFICIENCY BOOST -->
		<section class="features" id="features" data-demo-group="efficiency">
			<div class="features-inner">
				<div class="feat-head">
					<h2 class="feat-title">효율을 끌어올립니다</h2>
					<p class="feat-sub">정말 중요한 일에 시간을 쓰십시오.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="feat-demo-body">
					<div class="feat-list" role="tablist" aria-label="효율 향상 기능">
						{efficiencyFeatures.map((f, i) => (
							<button
								class="feat-item"
								type="button"
								role="tab"
								data-idx={i}
								aria-selected={i === 0 ? 'true' : 'false'}
								aria-controls={`efficiency-video-${i}`}
							>
								<div class="feat-item-head">
									<span class="feat-num">{String(i + 1).padStart(2, '0')}</span>
									<h3 class="feat-h">{f.title}</h3>
								</div>
								<p class="feat-p">{f.body}</p>
							</button>
						))}
					</div>
					<div class="feat-stage">
						<div class="feat-frame">
							{efficiencyFeatures.map((f, i) => (
								<video
									id={`efficiency-video-${i}`}
									class="feat-video"
									data-idx={i}
									src={f.video}
									muted
									loop
									playsinline
									preload={i === 0 ? 'auto' : 'metadata'}
									aria-hidden={i === 0 ? 'false' : 'true'}
								></video>
							))}
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- INTELLIGENT GHOSTWRITING -->
		<section class="features features-alt" data-demo-group="ghostwriting">
			<div class="features-inner">
				<div class="feat-head">
					<h2 class="feat-title">지능형 대필</h2>
					<p class="feat-sub">AI가 텍스트를 손쉽게 다듬어드립니다.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="feat-demo-body feat-demo-body--reverse">
					<div class="feat-stage">
						<div class="feat-frame">
							{ghostwritingFeatures.map((f, i) => (
								<video
									id={`ghostwriting-video-${i}`}
									class="feat-video"
									data-idx={i}
									src={f.video}
									muted
									loop
									playsinline
									preload="metadata"
									aria-hidden={i === 0 ? 'false' : 'true'}
								></video>
							))}
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="feat-list" role="tablist" aria-label="지능형 대필 기능">
						{ghostwritingFeatures.map((f, i) => (
							<button
								class="feat-item"
								type="button"
								role="tab"
								data-idx={i}
								aria-selected={i === 0 ? 'true' : 'false'}
								aria-controls={`ghostwriting-video-${i}`}
							>
								<div class="feat-item-head">
									<span class="feat-num">{String(i + 1).padStart(2, '0')}</span>
									<h3 class="feat-h">{f.title}</h3>
								</div>
								<p class="feat-p">{f.body}</p>
							</button>
						))}
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- USE CASES -->
		<section class="usecases">
			<div class="usecases-inner">
				<h2 class="usecases-head">다른 사람들은 Slax Note를 어떻게 쓰고 있을까요</h2>
				<div class="uc-grid">
					{useCases.map((uc) => (
						<div class="uc">
							<h3 class="uc-h">{uc.title}</h3>
							<p class="uc-p">{uc.body}</p>
						</div>
					))}
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- TESTIMONIALS -->
		<section class="testimonials">
			<div class="testimonials-inner">
				<h2 class="t-head">수많은 사용자가 사랑하는 도구</h2>
				<p class="t-sub">
					노트 작성을 혁신할 준비가 되셨나요? 지금 Slax Note를 써보십시오.
				</p>
				<div class="t-grid">
					{testimonials.map((t) => (
						<figure class="testimonial">
							<blockquote class="t-quote">"{t.quote}"</blockquote>
							<figcaption class="t-caption">
								<span class="t-author">{t.author}</span>
								<span class="t-title">{t.title}</span>
							</figcaption>
						</figure>
					))}
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- PRICING -->
		<section class="pricing" id="pricing">
			<div class="pricing-inner">
				<h2 class="pricing-head">가격</h2>
				<p class="pricing-dek">얼리버드 가격으로 플랜을 업그레이드해 보십시오.</p>

				<div class="plans-grid plans-grid-3">
					<!-- FREE -->
					<div class="plan">
						<div class="plan-eyebrow">Free</div>
						<div class="plan-price">
							<span class="num">$0</span>
						</div>
